---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Imaginary Interiors" description="About Imaginary Interiors — a visual atlas of interior design styles.">
  <div class="wrap">
    <section class="hero" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;padding-bottom:10px">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">About</div>
        <h1>About Imaginary Interiors</h1>
        <p class="sub">A visual atlas of interior design styles, rooms and palettes.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Imaginary Interiors helps people discover, name and recreate the interior styles they love
          through curated room concepts, palettes and practical shop-the-look ideas.</p>

        <h2>Our mission</h2>
        <p>
          Our mission is to make interior design language easier to see, compare and use. Whether
          you are planning a renovation, refreshing a single room or simply collecting inspiration,
          Imaginary Interiors gives you a visual way to understand styles, moods, materials and color
          combinations before you commit to a direction.</p>

        <h2>How we create the atlas</h2>
        <p>
          The site combines editorial curation with carefully composed imagery to turn design references
          into approachable room ideas. Each guide is organized around the details that matter in a
          real space: silhouettes, finishes, palettes, lighting, furniture choices and the small
          styling decisions that make a room feel intentional.</p>

        <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Visual style hubs for every major interior design style.</li>
          <li>Room-by-room ideas and color palettes.</li>
          <li>Trend guides and a quick style-matching quiz.</li>
          <li>Saved inspiration you can return to on the same device.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Get in touch</h2>
        <p>
          Questions, corrections or partnership ideas? Visit our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>
          and tell us what you are working on.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
